nodes.text: Spaceport Express was a small messenger service in Mos Eisley on Tatooine during the Galactic Civil War. It was run by the Quarren Omon Gantum who gladly accepted the offer from Gep's Grill to handle orders and deliveries.

At first, Spaceport Express only handled legal goods such as food and medicines. After the business deal with Norun Gep and Fillin Ta, the service became known for smuggling contraband such as stolen equipment or meat stuffed with contraband.
